  "text": "The 2Z quantization condition on the covering space T 6 is a Z quantization condition on T 6 /I 6 . It guarantees integer periods of F [CITATION_1] and H [CITATION_2] over cycles in T 6 /I 6 that descend from half-cycles in T 6 .",
